data.description: Drive up to this beautifully landscaped brick home. This home is in an established neighborhood with views of tall trees. Enter the home to view a great open floor plan with hard floors. The living room has amazing built ins around a cozy fireplace. This home has a fourth room that would be usable as a small bedroom or separate office with closet storage. The laudry room will make washing a breeze with a soaker sink! The master bathroom will make a great place to relax with a separate shower, soaker tub and a double sink counter. Book your showing today!
